- (UIColor *)stripeColorForChartType:(NSString *)value { id raw=value?:@"";NSString *type=[[raw description]uppercaseString];if([type isEqual:@"SIDPT"]||[type isEqual:@"STARPT"])return [UIColor colorWithWhite:.78 alpha:1];if([type hasPrefix:@"SID"])return [UIColor colorWithRed:.35 green:.72 blue:.35 alpha:1];if([type hasPrefix:@"STAR"])return [UIColor colorWithRed:1 green:.63 blue:.28 alpha:1];if([type isEqual:@"IAC"]||[type hasPrefix:@"APP"])return [UIColor colorWithRed:.29 green:.70 blue:.82 alpha:1];if([type isEqual:@"AFC"])return [UIColor colorWithRed:.68 green:.42 blue:.59 alpha:1];if([type isEqual:@"AGC"]||[type isEqual:@"APC"])return [UIColor colorWithRed:1 green:.65 blue:.52 alpha:1];if([type isEqual:@"LVC"])return [UIColor colorWithRed:.42 green:.66 blue:.83 alpha:1];if([type isEqual:@"MRC"])return [UIColor colorWithRed:.58 green:.80 blue:.86 alpha:1];if([type isEqual:@"AOI"])return [UIColor colorWithWhite:.78 alpha:1];if([type isEqual:@"ADC"]||[type isEqual:@"APT"])return [UIColor colorWithRed:.84 green:.70 blue:.39 alpha:1];return [UIColor colorWithWhite:.68 alpha:1]; }
